Scorponok


   Scorponok eye's shot with envy and anger. He thought to himself 
'Damn it, QuickStrike got 2nd in command. I used to have that honor. 
Why the slag did QuickStrike get 2nd in command? I, to my own 
knowledge was the best dang 2nd in command ever. I wish...I wish...I 
wish I could stick my missle into QuickStrike's Spark and fire it.' 

   He looked at Megatron and gritted his teeth. "Megatron do you have 
any orders for me?" Scorponok hoped that he wouldn't have to do 
anything with Quickstrike, that scum.
